1. *Primetili* smo da je kiša počela padati. (We noticed that the rain started to fall.)
2. Da li si *primetio* da je ovaj grad mnogo veći od našeg? (Did you notice that this city is much bigger than ours?)
3. Oni nisu *primetili* da su ostavili vrata otključana. (They didn't notice that they left the door unlocked.)
4. Kada sam *primetila* da je izgubila dragulje, pomogla sam joj da ih pronađe. (When I noticed that she lost her jewelry, I helped her find them.)
5. Nisam *primetio* da je neko prošao pored mene dok sam bio u parku. (I didn't notice that someone passed by me while I was in the park.)
6. Kada je *primetio* da joj se držanje promenilo, pitao ju je da li je sve u redu. (When he noticed that her posture changed, he asked her if everything was okay.)
7. Moraš biti pažljiv i *primetiti* sitne detalje ako želiš da budeš dobar detektiv. (You have to be careful and notice small details if you want to be a good detective.)
8. Ona je *primetila* da su joj cipele poderane tek kada je stigla na posao. (She noticed that her shoes were torn only when she arrived at work.)